Food Fighters US - Season 2, Episode 4




This Cheerleader's Got Game

Amber MacDonald, a former NFL cheerleader and now a stay-at-home mom from San Francisco, California puts her family recipes to the test. Amber's inspiration comes from her Sicilian grandma who taught her how to cook. The home chef wants to win the money to give back to her parents who have moved from Missouri to spend time with her two-year-old daughter Ava.




Original Air Date: 23-Jul-2015
